-- FORMOSA PLASTIC April Sales Fall 17.44% (Table) : 1301 TT
-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 2012-05-03T06:02:14Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-03/formosa-plastic-april-sales-fall-17-44-table-1301-tt.html
FORMOSA PLASTIC said unconsolidated sales
in April fell 17.44% to NT$15,042,522,000 from NT$18,220,577,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  4/2012           4/2011
Sales           15,042,522       18,220,577  
YOY%             -17.44%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           62,376,472       70,352,307  
YOY%             -11.34% 
=================================================================
 